resources.string:
Check logcat for error messages. Sometimes it can take a long time for SuperSU to prompt, and the test doesn't start until permission is granted.

Example logcat command:
adb logcat -s SIMFileSeekTest,RilExtender,RilExtenderCommandsInterface,AtCommandInterface,CommandsInterfaceFactory,TelephonySeekServiceCommandsInterface,SIMRecords,Parcel,librilinject,CMDProcessor,lib__hijack.bin__.so,System.err,su

If the commands are being received by the RilExtender, you might also check the radio log to see what the RIL is doing with them.
